{
  "stem": "15686.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was making ends meet, but it was hard for him to really support two extra boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to-- he enrolled us in a French school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had completed elementary school in Germany, so I had to go to what the French call lycee, which is sort of high school to start with.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it goes a little further than our American high schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to learn French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Fortunately, I've always had a good ear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I picked up French very quickly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It only took a few months, and I could really communicate fairly well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We stayed with my uncle until World War II broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it broke out between Germany and France and England on September 3, 1939.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now my uncle, being from Germany and had applied to become a French citizen, but the waiting period in France is seven years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he was not yet a French citizen, he was still German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And with that, he was now an enemy alien in France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the French rounded up the enemy aliens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because they couldn't tell which ones were good Germans and which ones were bad Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they rounded up the Jews with the other Gentile Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they put them into labor camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And their job was to repair roads, repair bridges, dig trenches for the troops, and do things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were not harmed in any way or threatened physically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they had to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With that of course, my aunt had no financial means to keep us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she called an acquaintance, who was working for a Jewish social agency in Paris called the [FRENCH], which means medical assistance group to help refugee children.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
